PEOPLE
v.
McCOY. No. S229296. Supreme Court of California July 27, 2016.

CANTIL-SAKAUYE, C.J., WERDEGAR, CHIN, CORRIGAN, LIU, CUÉLLAR, and KRUGER, JJ., concur.

Dismissed and remanded to CA 2/6. Review in the above-captioned matter, which was granted and held for People v. Morales (2016) 63 Cal.4th 399, 203 Cal.Rptr.3d 130, 371 P.3d 592, is hereby dismissed. (Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.528(b)(1).)
